WEBVTT

00:03:29.720 --> 00:03:31.880
on a cold Thursday morning

00:03:33.080 --> 00:03:36.040
for a crime that I hadn't committed.

00:03:37.160 --> 00:03:39.136
I remember holding

00:03:39.160 --> 00:03:42.080
my three-month-old beautiful daughter

00:03:43.080 --> 00:03:45.400
whom I had just named Oma,

00:03:46.280 --> 00:03:50.736
which in my dialect
means "truth and justice,"

00:03:50.760 --> 00:03:55.616
as that was what I had longed so much for

00:03:55.640 --> 00:03:56.840
all this time.

00:03:57.960 --> 00:04:01.576
I dressed her in her
favorite purple dress,